title: Indian Pumpkin & Veggie Dhal with Garlic Flatbreads & Coriander
description: Dhal is the ultimate bowl of goodness – rich in protein, a good source of fibre and full of aromatic flavours. The coconut milk balances the spices to create a meal that's both delectable and nourishing.

*Unfortunately, this
week's celery was in
short supply, so we've
replaced it with carrot.
Don't worry, the recipe
will be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow your
recipe card!*
